The '''''défilé d'Entre-Roches''''' is a canyon or gorge of the upper [[Doubs (river)|Doubs]] in the [[Departments of France|department]] of [[Doubs]] in eastern France.

[[Image:DefileDEntreRoches.jpg|thumb|left|Cliffs in the canyon]]

It extends about 30&nbsp;km along departmental highway 437 between [[Pontarlier]] and [[Morteau]].

